subSubSection.paragraph:
Female terminalia: Valves of oviscapt rounded at tip (particularly so in 
holotype
), ca. 280 µm long, with 17–20 marginal oviscapt pegs; length ca. 2.5× great width. Spermatheca cup-shaped, height approximately equal to width; basal introvert reaching about 0.7× length of capsule.
